<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <title>Clean4U(고객용)</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://site-assets.fontawesome.com/releases/v7.0.0/css/all.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components.css">
    {{#additionalCss}}
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{.}}">
    {{/additionalCss}}
</head>

<body class="client-page">
{{> layout/background}}

<div class="client-container">
    <div class="client-container-content">
        <div class="client-card">
            <div class="client-header">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-soap"></i>
                <h2>Clean4U 주문 조회</h2>
                <p>등록하신 전화번호로 주문 내역을 조회하실 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>

            <form id="client-form" class="client-form" onsubmit="handleFormSubmit(event)">
                <div class="client-input-group">
                    <label for="phone" class="client-label">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>
                        전화번호
                    </label>
                    <input
                            type="tel"
                            id="phone"
                            name="phone"
                            class="client-input"
                            placeholder="010-1234-5678 또는 01012345678"
                            required
                            pattern="[0-9\-]+"
                            maxlength="13">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-submit client-submit">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
                        주문 조회
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="client-footer">
                    <p>문의사항이 있으시면 매장으로 연락주세요.</p>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/phone-format.js"></script>
<script>
    function handleFormSubmit(event) {
        event.preventDefault();
        const phoneInput = document.getElementById('phone');
        const phone = phoneInput.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');
        if (phone) {
            window.location.href = '/client/' + encodeURIComponent(phone) + '/orders';
        }
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>